  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <div rend="parallel">
        <p xml:id="Aink256-kilavi">nī kūṟukiṉṟavaḷ niṉṉai varuttum paruvattaḷ allaḷ eṉṟa tōḻikkut talaimakaṉ colliyatu. </p>
        <p xml:lang="en">What the hero told the confidante who said, “The girl you speak of is not of the phase to torment you.”    
        </p>
      </div>
      <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink256">
<l>kuṉṟak kuṟavaṉ kātaṉ maṭamakaḷ</l>
<l>vaṇṭupaṭu kūntaṟ ṟaṇṭaḻaik koṭicci</l>
<l>vaḷaiyaṇ muḷaivā ḷeyiṟṟa</l>
<l>ḷiḷaiya ḷāyiṉu māraṇaṅ kiṉaḷē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
        <l>The beloved, naïve daughter</l>
        <l>of the hill-dweller—</l>
        <l rend="space">whose tresses have bees,</l>
        <l>who is like a creeper</l>
        <l>with cool foliage—</l>
        <l rend="space">she with bangles,</l>
        <l>she with sprouting, lustrous teeth—</l>
        <l rend="space">though she is young,</l>
        <l>is full of torment [for me].</l>
        
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
